Shiddat se nibhau wo aadat hai tu Ishq hi nahi rooh ki ibadat ho..!!

Meri nazar se kabhi khudko dekha lena tum khud hi khud pai fidaa ho jaogi..!!

Nigaho Se Tere Dil Par Paigam Likh Dun...Tum Kaho to Apni Rooh Tere Naam Likh Dun...!!!

Ek Tera Naam Rahe Zuban Par...Jaise Chand Rehta Hai Aasman Par...!!
